---
title: Cajun Spiced Beef Meatballs with cheesy mash and roasted broccoli
description: These Irish beef meatballs are infused with Cajun-inspired flavours for a subtle hint of spice. Served with perfectly tender broccoli and a hearty helping of cheesy mashed potato, this is a dish that is warming, comforting and will leave you wanting more.
